title: hub_guide__test_boss
---
<<if boss_cleared("mockingbird")>>
    Kernel Guide: boss_cleared("mockingbird") returned TRUE. The bird is retired — the cove dialogue switches to its after-treasure variant on your next pirate visit.
<<else>>
    Kernel Guide: boss_cleared("mockingbird") returned FALSE. The encounter is Dormant or InProgress — go pay the Admiral a visit and let him point you at the right rooftop.
<<endif>>
-> Back to test menu.
    <<jump hub_guide__test>>
===

title: hub_guide__test_visit
---
<<if visit_count("hub_guide") == 1>>
    Kernel Guide: visit_count("hub_guide") returned 1. First conversation this save.
<<else>>
    Kernel Guide: visit_count("hub_guide") returned more than 1. The counter pulls live from SandboxSaveData.dialog_visits — incremented every time DialogState.start fires with that id.
<<endif>>
-> Back to test menu.
    <<jump hub_guide__test>>
===

